<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="notice-n">notice <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'nəʊtɪs/    美 /'noʊtɪs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 注意：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It was Jenny who <strong>brought</strong> the problem <strong>to my notice</strong>.
是詹妮让我注意到这个问题的。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It has <strong>come to my notice</strong> that he was poor in health.
我开始注意到他身体不好。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The boss <strong>took no notice of the</strong> suggestion given by the clerk.
老板没理会员工提出的建议。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] 布告 (牌)；通告：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A notice was put up in order to remind the students of the changed lecture time.
为了提醒学生们讲座时间有变动，张贴了一张通告。</p><footer>2009 陕西</footer></div>

<h4 id="3-u">3.★ <strong>[U] 通知；预告：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Thanks for agreeing to see me <strong>at such short notice</strong>.
谢谢你一接到通知就同意见我。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This shop will be closed for repairs <strong>until further notice</strong>.  
本店因修缮停止营业，开业时间另行通知。</p><footer>2011 全国</footer></div></div>